{"tid":527063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傑志新援烏拉圭球星科蘭科蘭廣東話冧球迷：選擇來港因樂於迎接新挑戰","createTime":"2018-01-12T09:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T16:06:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"87cd1e52ba974f7695e9e33e1c1f619f6613b53b","tid":527063,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180112/s00006/1e0030acb3534a43150856a539a8081b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180112%2Fs00006%2F1e0030acb3534a43150856a539a8081b.jpg&h=5981c95d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180112/s00006/1515735275143\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180112%2Fs00006%2F1515735275143&d=ZLlp%2BqdNaSGF4Tu9lAAn4ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2e5042bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180112%2Fs00006%2F1515735275143&h=c413822a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180112/s00006/1515735275143</a><br />\n<br />\n烏拉圭球星科蘭殺到香港第2天，今午以傑志新援身分現身紅磡，出席球隊進軍亞冠盃之旅記者會。38歲的他吸引半百傳媒到訪，坐下來不久便以廣東話說「我會加油」冧球迷，自言步入職業球員生涯第20年，選擇來港是樂於迎接新挑戰，更多次自信強調自己雖久疏戰陣，但狀態依然，盼與傑志在亞冠踢出佳績。<br />\n<br />\n2010年世界盃金球獎得主科蘭空降傑志，昨日抵埗後急急離開，今日現身記者會首度開腔，全程面帶笑容表現友善，當球會總經理吳凱威搞笑以廣東話問他心情時，他更似懂非懂地以廣東話說「我會加油」。被問及為何選擇來港時，科蘭表示：「這是我步入職業球員生涯第20年，我很想繼續迎接挑戰。身為球員就會不斷周遊列國，我有從廣州朋友口中了解香港，很期待來港生活，並與傑志出戰亞冠盃。」<br />\n<br />\n38歲的科蘭表示，昨日從機場回到寓所，沿途看到風景極像日本，很有親切感，又指自己雖長時間未有比賽，但自言狀態十足：「自己踢了多年，技術肯定不成問題，只是體能狀態要努力提升，但我相信不是問題，亦會盡力去做好。」傑志將於2月展開亞冠分組賽之旅，首階段球迷會會員可以$60至$180優惠價，於1月17日晚上11時優先訂票，其他球迷可於1月22日預售2月20日對全北汽車一戰，售價為$100、$250及$300。而傑志港超主場票價亦會提升至$50、$150，球迷會會員票價不變。"},{"pid":"af45148adae5bc87f900f6dc5e42e6056e6d91ad","tid":527063,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:58:52.000Z","msg":"挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f5433d4fec7a1a8d93295fe212cd62cf87977e","tid":527063,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T13:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32c1a428ee13ad68f4680a049639a787ac1fcc3","tid":527063,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:16:46.000Z","msg":"真折墜 晚節不保"},{"pid":"6a90698233711ee73b9b63752443413b9f526210","tid":527063,"uid":72399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"港足有咩挑戰？"},{"pid":"71f89523a2472ade0169b4c5221ec785f2b3131f","tid":527063,"uid":19762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:21:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d9ZPtXYFHz4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd9ZPtXYFHz4&d=ZLlp%2BqdNaSGF4Tu9lAAn4ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=aa056ef2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d9ZPtXYFHz4</a>"},{"pid":"2a1cb3c60fb1903fb524da0153c411b73fcc04b0","tid":527063,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:21:56.000Z","msg":"落老蘭挑戰港女？"},{"pid":"87252231d13235331f4ef40727bbdad523a9b206","tid":527063,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港足有咩挑戰？</blockquote><br />\n1晚砌3條港女，要砌足成年，好大挑戰"},{"pid":"4fbf677306c30b7493964b09b3672a624c8f0ef9","tid":527063,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:22:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cb5d445e549c384e039b6070be6ef8df83681bc","tid":527063,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:24:17.000Z","msg":"想去現場睇一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8546500c24221ff005d611e9f89e81488c6817c8","tid":5270